@startuml
title delegateRole(from, to, roleName) Flow

actor Caller
participant PermissionPolicy
participant ManagerAssignment

Caller -> PermissionPolicy : delegateRole(from, to, roleName)

PermissionPolicy -> PermissionPolicy : findAssignment(from) : ManagerAssignment
PermissionPolicy -> ManagerAssignment : hasRole(roleName)

alt 위임 가능
  ManagerAssignment --> PermissionPolicy : true
  PermissionPolicy --> PermissionPolicy : assignRole(to, roleName)
  PermissionPolicy --> Caller : void

else 위임 불가
  ManagerAssignment --> PermissionPolicy : false
  PermissionPolicy -> Caller : throw ForbiddenException
end
@enduml